snippet.title: MLB The Show 25 - Official Cover Athletes Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Watch the Cover Athletes Reveal Trailer for MLB The Show 25, the latest addition to the legendary baseball simulation game developed by Sony San Diego. Paul Skenes, Elly De La Cruz, and Gunnar Henderson will grace the cover of MLB The Show 25, check out the trailer to see their reactions to being a part of MLB The Show history. MLB The Show 25 is launching on March 18 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and Nintendo Switch.
